## 2. Data Layer — RoomData.cs & Enums

### RoomData — ScriptableObject

```csharp
[CreateAssetMenu(fileName = "New Room", menuName = "Procedural Generation/Room Data")]
public class RoomData : ScriptableObject
{
    public GameObject roomPrefab;         // Prefab (không dùng trong auto-gen mode)
    public RoomType roomType;             // Start, Archetype1, MidBoss, Boss, Goal...
    public Vector2Int size = Vector2Int.one; // Kích thước trên grid
    public List<DoorAnchor> doorAnchors;  // Config các cửa
    public int maxTrapSpawnPoints = 3;
    public float enemySpawnRate = 0.5f;
}
```

> [!IMPORTANT]
> [RoomData](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Data/RoomData.cs#9-39) là **ScriptableObject** — tạo trong Unity Editor qua menu "Procedural Generation/Room Data". Mỗi loại phòng có 1 asset riêng. Code **KHÔNG modify** ScriptableObject khi chạy, mà dùng `actualSize` override trong [Room](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Core/Room.cs#37-50).

