**Câu hỏi**: *Tại sao dùng `[System.Serializable]` cho [DoorAnchor](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Data/RoomData.cs#58-73)?*
→ Vì [DoorAnchor](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Data/RoomData.cs#58-73) không phải MonoBehaviour hay ScriptableObject, nó là plain class. `[Serializable]` cho phép Unity serialize nó bên trong [RoomData](file:///e:/%21FPT/7.SP26/PRU213/NoWayOut/Assets/Scripts/ProceduralGeneration/Data/RoomData.cs#9-39) để hiện trong Inspector.

